This original dataset has 152655 loci and 533 individuals

frequency of individuals with 1+ reads per individual - raw

lociperind <- colSums(dat>0)
hist(lociperind,main=paste("number of loci per ind; ",dim(dat)[1],"loci"),xlab="",breaks=20)

lociperind.freq <- colSums(dat>0)/dim(dat)[1]
